snippet.title: Character Teaser - "Furina: Member of the Cast" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
"In real life, we've all seen flowers wilt, been caught out in the rain, and heard of ships being lost without a trace...
But despite all this, there's something that I am convinced is still worth believing —
That, at least on the stage, people's fate is in their own hands."
